Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyokaku Kumoi\Nhas grown impatient
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the failed attempts\Nto assassinate Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He bestows his veteran assassin\Nand his squad members
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with powerful swords\Nknown as the Bakkouto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:45.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,forged through\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan’s hidden art,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and dispatches them\Nto the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo battles Hanza Nukui,\Nthe leader of the assassin squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:55.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the knowledge gained\Nfrom their previous fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:58.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo targets\Nthe Bakkouto Saiga’s weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:03.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, he finds himself trapped\Ninside a world of mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:12.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never fall for\Nthe same move twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:29.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Zanpakuto derives its attack\Nfrom reflected light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:32.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I shatter that, it’s all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:49.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, depending on\Nthe Spiritual Pressure of its wielder,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:51.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,this sword can get\Ninfinitely stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:18.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s not good,\Nboys don’t cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me Ichigo…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What made you want to\Nlearn karate all of a sudden?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s a secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, you don’t\Nwant to tell your mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look, look, that’s so pretty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:38.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You’re right! So pretty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo, do you like sunsets?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They’re pretty,\Nbut I don’t like them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start feeling a little lonely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s not so! They’re pretty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:38.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki.\NThis is the true power of my Saiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:47.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give you a good taste\Nof your worst nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t like sunsets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back…Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m sorry, Ichigo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– Why?{\i0}\N– Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t find you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:55.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I was just a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:11.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just that, back then I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of what I did…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:24.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let’s go home.\NEveryone’s worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My body…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn’t right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She died!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:27.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This…is not reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not over.\NIt’s just beginning, Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:47.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This nightmare will continue\Nuntil you go mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:01.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it…Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:10.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an illusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! This…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really think this is\Nenough to bring me down?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Ntry to take her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:27.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother…\NSee if you can kill your loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, your resolve cannot\Ncompare to the likes of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who have chosen\Nthe path of blood and strife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s over…Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:41.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s…that black\NSpiritual Pressure again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:49.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s…fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:17.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Yuzu and Karin.\NAnd Dad is his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:21.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m…all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m getting by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are escaping the nightmare\Ncreated by Saiga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you\Nhave such power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:51.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…back then…I…\Ncouldn’t protect you, I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:57.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.\NThanks…for protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:20.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to step all over\Nsomeone else’s memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You… You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:15.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you…being consumed\Nby your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bakkouto…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The more spiritual power you pour in…\Nit’s power…will grow infinitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:42.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:51.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You… Why fight that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:56.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the Kasumiohji Clan…\Nand for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:02.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since ancient times, the Kasumiohji Clan\Nhas been a distinguished clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,proudly providing swords\Nto the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:11.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We too have historically existed\Nalongside them as their shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And at times…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We would even deceive the Thirteen\NCourt Guard Squads themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep the hidden art behind\Nour sword making technique safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it were forbidden…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:00.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all to protect\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That has been\Nour reason for existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:13.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amongst them, I have fought\Nmany bitter battles and survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I acquired this power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:26.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A power only\Nthe chosen few are granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re saying you are\Nthe chosen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right! Then you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:47.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If your purpose in being is to\Nprotect the Kasumiohji Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you attack Rurichiyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:54.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the weak have no right\Nto carry on the Kasumiohji legacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:04.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo is…\Nfrightened…shaking…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she’s smiling,\Nshe’s afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:12.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She…just wants to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess of the Kasumiohji Clan\Nhas no freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…not something\Nfor you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:59.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s…your…true…power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not going to lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not the chosen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just consumed\Nby that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:18.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t…be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:26.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that thing…\NYou’re just shortening your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:27.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the limit\Nof my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:37.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Bakkouto would\Nnever consume me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it’s impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but I’m sure—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Kibune!\NGreetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But he’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:23.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should get\NLieutenant Hisagi’s advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune…\NWhere is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Third Seat Kibune here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:05.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the lavatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:09.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a maze.\NI can’t remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… I’m trying to\Nfind the lavatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kannogi is the master here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why has he been left alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Escort him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:29.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me!\NI’m looking for the lavatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:49.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Genga is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Nukui and Douko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:06.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This…is quite a sharp sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Nukui and\Nmy brothers are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:11.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\NI’ll take Nukui’s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:21.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have nothing to do with\Na small fish like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, how are Ishida\Nand the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:26.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Recovering, but he suddenly\Nfell unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:29.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To help him feel better,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave him some chazuke\Nwith ohagi mixed into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:40.48,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MEN’S SOUL REAPER ASSOCIATION\N	MEN’S LAVATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A joint activity with\N	the Women’s Association?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:44.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, today we received an official\Nrequest from Vice-Chairman Ise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:49.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means they finally recognize\Nthe Men’s Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:51.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let’s participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in charge of—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For verbal threats\Nsuch as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:00.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it is imperative to react\Nwith a firm disposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:05.01,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WOMEN’S SOUL REAPER ASSOCIATION\N	"HOW TO REJECT A HARD SELL" SEMINAR
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:02.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:07.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,